| 2 | single live cell dies | ✅ |
| 3 | dead cell with 3 neighbors is born (forced real logic) | ✅ |
| 4 | two adjacent cells die (underpopulation) | ✅ |
| 5 | live cell with 2–3 neighbors survives | ✅ |
| 6 | live cell with >3 neighbors dies (overpopulation) | ✅ |
| 7 | negative coordinates | ✅ |
